    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Hatake Clan are extremely proficient Chakra molders. They innately have the ability to call upon a unique source of Chakra called White Chakra. </p><p>Beginning at 1st level, you have 5 White Chakra which you can only spend on Jutsu with the Lightning Release keyword. You gain 1 White Chakra every level. When you finish a short rest you regain half of your spent White Chakra. Your White Chakra pool is fully refilled on a long rest</p>",
